# Terraform — never commit state, lock files, provider binaries, or user-specific values.
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
**/.terraform.tfstate.lock.info
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.backup
**/terraform.tfvars

